            <span class="utterance" who="#weinbergJ" start="224.490" end="x">. . . And then . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="225.243" end="x">Yes . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Julian Weinberg</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#weinbergJ" start="225.665" end="x">. . . our plant was taken over by an <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> man . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
