            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1521.085" end="x">For what purpose?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Julian Weinberg</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#weinbergJ" start="1523.646" end="x">These old pieces of clothing should be used by the Jews who had still remained, because . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1530.194" end="x">[word not clear]</span>
