            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1880.907" end="x">. . . pillows and [In English:] bedding, [the confusion of the language by the interviewee obviously affects also the interviewer; like in the case of a normal individual talking to a stutterer—again in German] bedclothes.</span>
